Humility is essential in healthy bonding, for it allows you to appreciate another person. Healthy bonding is the union of two distinct people, with independent personalities, who join for a higher purpose than satisfying their own needs.
When performing your next prayer, thank God for helping you bond with specific individuals.
Today is Forty Days, which is Five Weeks and Five Days of the Omer.
Hayom arbaim ve'chamishah yom la'omer.